bgm.name: 10日常パート・放課後等落ち着いたシーン

parameters: Yui: "Today is a date with Ginga♪ I'm so excited~!"

Polka: "Yui-chan, don't get too carried away! If we don't hurry, we'll
be late to meet up with Ginga."
Polka: "You don't want to be disliked by your beloved Ginga, do you?"
Yui: "I know that~. I'm about to go now."
Polka: "It's at the pool in the Forus district, right?"
Yui: "Yeah. Ginga said it's hot today, so let's go to the pool."

Polka: "Then, maybe I should go too~. I haven't seen Ginga in a while,
and I want to see him in his swimsuit~"

Polka: "Hehehe, just kidding, just kidding. I wouldn't dream of
interrupting your lovey-dovey pool date."
Yui: "I-it's not like I mind if Polka comes along, okay?"

Polka: "But you were seriously picking out underwear, weren't you?
You're probably hoping something might happen after the date, right?"

Polka: "I knew it, I knew it~! Even I wouldn't interfere that much~
Hehehe!"
Yui: "...I-I'm not thinking about that sort of thing..."
Yui: "...Today is just a d-date, that's all."

Polka: "Yes, yes! I got it. Enjoy yourself to the fullest in this
peaceful town!"

Polka: "The town you saved is brimming with fun. It would be a waste
not to enjoy it."
Polka: "The one who should be saying thanks is me."

Polka: "Let me say it again, thank you so much for saving this town!
The kind-hearted hero, Morisaki Yui-chan!"
Polka: "Come on, you'll be late for your meetup. Hurry up, hurry up!"
Yui: "Right, I'm going now. Please take care of the house, Polka!"
Polka: "...while saying that~, time for some reconnaissance! Hehehe!"
